# Small talk

Wie gehts? > How's it going?
Gut > Good
Sehr gut > Very good
Prima > Great
Super > Great
Schlecht > Bad
Sehr schlecht > Very bad
Soso > Indifferent

Wie gehts es dir? > How goes it to you? OR How are you?
Wie > How
Gehts > Goes
Es > It
Dir > To you
Gut, und wie gehts es dir > Good, and how are you?
Wie gehts es Ihnen? > How goes it to you? OR How are you? (formal)
Ihnen > To you (a show of respect) OR to them
Nicht schlecht > Not bad
